- - - - -

CalibrationControl is modified to allow mode 1 and 2 if it is running in on international station and if the RemoteStation.conf file contains a key RS.N_FOREIGN_ANTENNAS that has a value > 0.

The low level class stationconfig is aware of this new optional key, the value is available via the variable nrForeignAnts.

